# Large vendored Terminal-Wrench build-context data assets (e.g. fMRIdata.RData,
# ~80MB) are regenerated by `python -m forkproof.qabench.materialize` from the
# pinned Terminal-Wrench checkout and are pinned by digest in each env's
# provenance.json (build_context_digest). Keep them out of git history. See README.md.
**/*.RData
